data.title: Music Under the Stars™ will return May 12, 2024!
data.meta_description: The Tucson Pops Orchestra has been sharing the joy of live music with audiences of all ages since 1955. Music Under the Stars™ will return May 12, 2024 with guest artist Gabriel Ayala.
data.text:
Our upcoming Fall Concert Series starts SOON!!!

Please join us for the following concert dates at the

DeMeester Outdoor Performing Arts Center @ Reid Park

Sunday, September 22, 2024 - 7 pm

Sunday, September 29, 2024 - 7 pm

Sunday, October 6, 2024 - 7 pm

The Tucson Pops Orchestra has been sharing the joy of live music with audiences of all ages since 1955.

SAAFB FOOD TRUCK RALLY

SAAFB (Southern Arizona Animal Food Bank) coordinates the food trucks for the concert series. To date, SAAFB has helped over 800 families throughout Southern Arizona who need help caring for their pets by giving more than 100,000 pounds of animal food. Donations of a bag of animal feed would be greatly appreciated. To learn more please visit saafb.org.
